### delete a catalog by id
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/catalogs/c0c7caa6-cc95-4a65-9688-05706b11b986
Content-Type: application/json

### get a catalog with by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalogs/f1bd6f58-bb37-4552-a539-fe3fe15ece06
