### get a catalog by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalogs?name=Computer%20Electronics
Content-Type: application/json

### get a catalog with slug
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalogs?slug=computer_electronic
Content-Type: application/json

### get all catalogs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalogs
Content-Type: application/json

### get all catalogs ordered
GET http://localhost:8080/api/catalogs/ordered
Content-Type: application/json

### get a catalog with its root categories by id
